      "instruction": "<p>Remove the stalk from your <strong>dried ancho chilli[es] </strong>and discard</p><p>Add<strong> </strong>the<strong> dried ancho chilli[es] </strong>to a bowl</p><p>Cover with 200ml <span class=\"text-purple\">[300ml]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[400ml]</span> <strong>boiled water</strong> and set aside for 5 min to soften</p><p>While the ancho chilli is softening, trim the green stalk off your <strong>aubergine[s] </strong>and discard, then chop into bite-sized pieces</p>",
      "order": 3,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-3-1672853517935-x200.jpg",
