    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add your<strong> tortillas</strong> to the reserved baking tray</p><p>Put the tray in the oven for 2-3 min or until they're warmed through</p><p>While the tortillas are in the oven, crumble your <strong>feta </strong>roughly</p><p>Wash your<strong> lettuce</strong>, then pat it dry with kitchen paper and shred finely</p>",
