    {
      "instruction": "<p>Divide the<strong> shredded lettuce</strong>,<strong> salsa roja</strong> and <strong>remaining diced tomato</strong> evenly between the<strong> tortillas</strong> and top with the <strong>suadero-style spiced aubergine</strong> and<strong> crumbled feta</strong></p><p>Tear over your <strong>coriander</strong> and garnish with the <strong>chilli rounds </strong>(not a fan of spice? Just add a little!)</p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
